<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Paginator should offer setDefaultItemCountPerPage().</p>

<p>Scenario:
Someone is using Zend_Paginator in his project and suddenly realizes that he don't want default 10 items per page, but he didn't use $paginator-&gt;setDefaultItemCountPerPage(10) - so he can't use replace.</p>

<p>How it should work:
Zend_Paginator::setDefaultItemCountPerPage(int $count); //would change from 10 to $count</p>

